<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/aislinn-rice> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Dr Aislinn Rice has over 25 years’ experience in leadership positions across small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) and global organisations in the technology sector. She was appointed to the Board of QUBIS from 2012 to 2018, the commercialisation arm of Queen’s University Belfast ( QUB ). Aislinn is currently Director of Software NI and Non-Executive Director at Analytics Engines. She holds a PhD in Chemistry from QUB .  More recently, Aislinn was awarded with the Digital DNA Special Recognition Award for continued commitment and contribution to the NI Technology ecosystem. She was named as 2025’s Outstanding Woman in Tech at the Northern Ireland Women in Tech Awards."@en .
